g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: upp-configure-slider-method (slider : class uil-slider) pointer : class uil-slider-pointer = the uil-slider-pointer that is the-pointer-in slider; C : class uil-slider-configuration-class ; begin if the uil-slider-configuration-class named by the configuration of slider exists then begin C = the uil-slider-configuration-class named by the configuration of slider; if the state of slider is enabled then begin change the color-pattern of slider so that uil-slider-background-color = the uil-slider-background-color of C, uil-slider-border-color = the uil-slider-border-color of C, uil-slider-light-color = the uil-slider-light-color of C, uil-slider-dark-color = the uil-slider-dark-color of C; change the color-pattern of pointer so that uil-slider-background-color = the uil-slider-background-color of C, uil-slider-border-color = the uil-slider-border-color of C, uil-slider-light-color = the uil-slider-light-color of C, uil-slider-dark-color = the uil-slider-dark-color of C end else begin change the color-pattern of slider so that uil-slider-background-color = the uil-slider-disabled-color of C, uil-slider-border-color = the uil-slider-border-color of C, uil-slider-light-color = the uil-slider-disabled-color of C, uil-slider-dark-color = the uil-slider-disabled-color of C; change the color-pattern of pointer so that uil-slider-background-color = the uil-slider-disabled-color of C, uil-slider-border-color = the uil-slider-border-color of C, uil-slider-light-color = the uil-slider-disabled-color of C, uil-slider-dark-color = the uil-slider-disabled-color of C; end; end; end
upp-get-slider-value (Slider : class uil-slider) = (quantity) begin return the current-value of Slider; end

g2:c.RULE.g2:a.TEXT: whenever any uil-slider slider is moved by the user and when the uil-slider-creation-flag of slider is ok then start upp-move-slider (slider)
whenever any uil-slider-pointer P is moved by the user then start upp-adjust-slider-value (the uil-slider that is the-container-for P)
whenever any uil-slider slider is moved by the user and when the uil-slider-creation-flag of slider is newly-created then start upp-post-creation-processing (slider)
whenever the uil-slider-creation-flag flag of any uil-slider slider receives a value and when flag is newly-created and the workspace of slider exists then start upp-post-creation-processing (slider)

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: _uilslide-toggle-user-menu-choices (B: class uil-button, W: class item, D-or-W: class item) begin if (the toggle-state of B is on) then conclude that uilslide-user-menu-choices-active is true else conclude that uilslide-user-menu-choices-active is false; end
